<div class="comment" id="comment5944">
  <p class="banner"><a href="/web/20081122152809/http://ja.doukaku.org/user/88/" target="_top">sumim</a><a href="/web/20081122152809/http://ja.doukaku.org/qa/#medal" target="_top"><img src="/web/20081122152809im_/http://ja.doukaku.org/static/image/star_gold.png" border=0/></a><a href="/web/20081122152809/http://ja.doukaku.org/qa/#anomark" target="_top"><img src="/web/20081122152809im_/http://ja.doukaku.org/static/image/anomark.png" border=0/></a>

	
	&nbsp;
	<a href="/web/20081122152809/http://ja.doukaku.org/comment/5944/">#5944</a>(<script language="JavaScript">print_time(new Date("2008/03/05 10:30 GMT"));</script><noscript>2008/03/05 10:30 GMT</noscript>)
	
	
	
	[<a href="/web/20081122152809/http://ja.doukaku.org/lang/smalltalk/">
	  Smalltalk
	</a>]
	
	
	
	&nbsp;

<span class="rating">Rating<span style="background-color: #ffffff;">0/0=0.00</span></span>
  </p>
  <div class="comment_content" >
	<div class="comment_body">
	  <p>Squeak Smalltak では変数の初期値が nil なので、nil の場合のみブロックを実行する #ifNil: を適宜コールして初期化などを行ないます。</p>

	</div>
	
	
	
    <div class="compact">
      <table><tr><td class="linenos"><pre>1</pre></td><td class="code"><div class="highlight"><pre>foo ifNil: [foo := &#39;hoge&#39;]
</pre></div>
</td></tr></table>
