<div class="comment" id="comment5981">
  <p class="banner"><a href="/web/20081122152809/http://ja.doukaku.org/user/685/" target="_top">Nemo</a><a href="/web/20081122152809/http://ja.doukaku.org/qa/#anomark" target="_top"><img src="/web/20081122152809im_/http://ja.doukaku.org/static/image/anomark.png" border=0/></a>

	
	&nbsp;
	<a href="/web/20081122152809/http://ja.doukaku.org/comment/5981/">#5981</a>(<script language="JavaScript">print_time(new Date("2008/03/07 14:19 GMT"));</script><noscript>2008/03/07 14:19 GMT</noscript>)
	
	
	
	[<a href="/web/20081122152809/http://ja.doukaku.org/lang/postscript/">
	  PostScript
	</a>]
	
	
	
	&nbsp;

<span class="rating">Rating<span style="background-color: #ffffff;">0/0=0.00</span></span>
  </p>
  <div class="comment_content" >
	<div class="comment_body">
	  <pre class='compact'>PostScript における「変数」というのが微妙なところですが、
カレント辞書に名前と値のペアを登録することだと解釈しました。

GS&gt;/a 10 def
GS&gt;/a 20 DefaultValue 
GS&gt;/b 30 DefaultValue 
GS&gt;a =
10
GS&gt;b =
30
</pre>
	</div>
	
	
	
    <div class="compact">
      <table><tr><td class="linenos"><pre>1
2
3
4
5
6
7
8</pre></td><td class="code"><div class="highlight"><pre>%!PS
/DefaultValue { % Symbol val DefaultValue -
  currentdict 2 index known {
    pop pop
  } {
    def
  } ifelse
} bind def
</pre></div>
</td></tr></table>
    </div>
	

  
